Package: TrackLandscapeR
Type: Package
Title: Scaled Multi-Track Genomic Density Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Liurxx", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Provides a publication-ready workflow to bin genomic interval
    data, apply per-track proportional scaling, and render aligned area
    plots for multiple tracks on the same chromosome. Includes helper
    functions, sample data, and a vignette demonstrating typical usage.
